{"tid":2383273,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[ling嘢長文] （有錯重開）嫌自己個名太普通，想霸氣啲","createTime":"2021-01-27T20:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:49:06.000Z","uid":302951,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7984e4390355e123810534fa9b859c1290601e60","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:14:22.000Z","msg":"建議睇咗上一篇先<br />\n[ling嘢長文] 其實埃及象形字幾似中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2381250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2381250</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓豬樓豬，我嫌腦魔Lomore太普通，想要個霸氣啲嘅名，你有咩建議？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：埃及象形文字──聖書體夠唔夠霸氣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：夠啊！點寫㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：簡單嚟講，我地參考下圖，用表音符號盡量還原你個名嘅讀，有啲似將Mary譯做瑪莉咁。幅圖涵括大部分單音符號，應該夠大家用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZHHwaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZHHwaQ.png&h=27c41f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpCsHhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpCsHhM.png&h=1dc47057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1/ 抽取子音（aeiou以外嘅音）<br />\n例：A<span class=\"red\">l</span>e<span class=\"red\">x</span> &gt;&gt;&gt; l x<br />\n<br />\n2/ 檢查有無埃及文字缺少嘅音，有就用近音代替<br />\n例：l <span class=\"red\">x</span> &gt;&gt;&gt; l k s<br />\n<br />\n3/ 補返啲無咗唔得嘅母音<br />\n例：l k s &gt;&gt;&gt; <span class=\"red\">A</span> l k s<br />\n（咩叫無咗唔得？通常係字頭字尾 <span class=\"red\">A</span>lice Sandr<span class=\"red\">a</span> <span class=\"red\">A</span>m<span class=\"red\">y</span><br />\n如果都係唔明，可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n4/ 換做象形文字，完成！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例：A l k s &gt;&gt;&gt; 禿鷹 獅子 籃 門閂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有幾樣嘢要注意：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 紅色嘅符號係後期先出現嘅寫法，你可以跟據個人喜好，選擇採用舊式或者新式。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 一個名可以有幾種譯法，就好似Mary可以係瑪莉、瑪利、瑪麗、馬莉、馬利、馬麗。<br />\n<br />\n3/ 聖書體係一種好着重美感嘅文字，如果你個名夠長，可以喺唔影響閱讀順序嘅情況下，疊起啲符號。<br />\n<br />\n4/ 呢篇剩係教音譯，意譯因為樓豬修行未夠高，教唔到大家。唔巧意思！"},{"pid":"2fdd1f3b271285de29a98b0865ae9f2185276f3c","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Lomore可以拆做lo-more兩個音節，轉寫做n-m-a，分別係波浪、新 &bull; 貓頭鷹、同手臂。喺最尾加返個男仔符號，表示呢抽係人名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbEF2Pk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbEF2Pk.png&h=9cadef2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我叫Minnie，個名又會係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：m-n-Y，貓頭鷹、波浪、新 &bull; 蘆葦，加女仔符號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5VRpAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5VRpAC.png&h=4bfed6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁我呢？我叫Minmin啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢個情況特別啲，你當然可以用四個單音m-n-m-n，但係亦可以用兩個雙音mn-mn，睇落短啲。最後加返神嘅符號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjk6dWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqjk6dWS.png&h=e7666744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就係咁啦！大家可以試下砌自己個名，唔識砌嘅，可以喺下面問。如果你個名好特別嘅，小心唔好自爆。"},{"pid":"a8c1e8a1fc636a020f1721c4ce29a43f36c6d9d5","tid":2383273,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>𓂸</strong></span> 我叫dicky"},{"pid":"f22c2a30a89234d787e55218d768a885844bc1a0","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a8c1e8a1fc636a020f1721c4ce29a43f36c6d9d5","tid":2383273,"uid":11598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>𓂸</strong></span> 我叫dicky"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T20:32:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">𓂺</span> dicky （已射）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">你嗰條屌讀做mt</span>"},{"pid":"c93b61c909edd1b94e07befb196d6a710c9f4a8c","tid":2383273,"uid":257438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"啲音同阿拉伯文差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a735099cf3ba76abcca968075cbed75bd69da884","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4a4c4132c6f3000d09ed61a760d381211e5ccb","tid":2383273,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"麵麵最後加返神嘅符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07fc6503e846b4574c57899418add348c266cd8","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be4a4c4132c6f3000d09ed61a760d381211e5ccb","tid":2383273,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"麵麵最後加返神嘅符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"麵麵係超越男女凡人肉體嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b13594514f5bead0f4b92ea282c88486b99687d","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93b61c909edd1b94e07befb196d6a710c9f4a8c","tid":2383273,"uid":257438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"啲音同阿拉伯文差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"佢地係近親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網聽字母讀音嗰陣，好多時候會搵返希伯來文同阿拉伯文嘅片做參考"},{"pid":"6121c6683c2f293c24fa1d76a9cfcea7e4718a19","tid":2383273,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"呢個係表音啫, 個意可以點樣知<br />\n<br />\n係好似中文咁表意定係字母咁砌字, 睇既方法又係咁, 長文同壁畫又有無分別, 即係畫面語, 詩詞, 專名組合<br />\n<br />\n仲有寫字果陣既公仔同壁畫公仔又有無分別<br />\n<br />\n砌字個上下大細又係點玩"},{"pid":"7ae3097c7d31ed570ee9ed8736bf85260be464d5","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6121c6683c2f293c24fa1d76a9cfcea7e4718a19","tid":2383273,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"呢個係表音啫, 個意可以點樣知<br />\n<br />\n係好似中文咁表意定係字母咁砌字, 睇既方法又係咁, 長文同壁畫又有無分別, 即係畫面語, 詩詞, 專名組合<br />\n<br />\n仲有寫字果陣既公仔同壁畫公仔又有無分別<br />\n<br />\n砌字個上下大細又係點玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"因為就咁音譯人名，所以唔涉及意思。例如譯Mary做馬利時，我地唔會當佢係馬嘅利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意譯就好似你中文名叫阿康，然後譯做埃及文字嘅健康。呢個真係要對佢啲字詞有一定認識先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫字同壁畫嘅分別，你當好似我地揸筆寫字同電腦字體咁，嚴謹程度有別。<br />\n<br />\n砌字同本身粒字嘅結構有關，但係有一定自由度。橫書時，兩個扁 (n r) 嘅可以上下疊起。而直書時，兩個窄嘅 (s i) 可以左右夾埋，有啲特別嘅排列組合要靠睇多啲就會知（可以參考上一篇「這個神說公牛出現在天上」，最尾有個三個符號嘅組合<br />\n𓊪 𓏏 𓇯）<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2b778de95dd4beaba1232d829aaed3c86d6ed0","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"除咗之有位巴打話楔形文字，想知大家仲對咩topic有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbd7dcf1e88f2314672af802f8cf5b81e083e91","tid":2383273,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a1cc0984ede2b64e698aab377f8db8d9e34e8d5","tid":2383273,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b726dd4320e4ce3b555e2e25b20d1147cdbe412f","tid":2383273,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4319a6b181e105d3f55b370f89fb8e4fc4b974","tid":2383273,"uid":128716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"麵神知唔個有依個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7717e085c3d7ef7a7ed69ba143f32002f5fed037","tid":2383273,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac4319a6b181e105d3f55b370f89fb8e4fc4b974","tid":2383273,"uid":128716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"麵神知唔個有依個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"好似唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到佢睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e10e984aeb2f1ee46c07b840af13daa539049","tid":2383273,"uid":281053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bf5694602c5e49cadbf2dfdca76c4d66725f972","tid":2383273,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/joTXuZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?